data.description: $20,000 PRICE DROP from list...NOW $359,900!!!   LOCATION-LOCATION-LOCATION!!!       Need space for kids/pets to run and play? This 1.08 acre level lot offers just that. LOOK AT THIS LARGE LOT!!! Fenced back yard. High-demand North Pointe Elementary/TL Hanna HS zone. Don't let this one get away from you. This 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath with a BONUS and home OFFICE is a dream in this market at $359,900!!!  Rocking chair front porch plus a spacious screened porch overlooking the backyard. You will want to spend much time enjoying the screened porch.  Deck. 2-car attached garage. Sidewalks to front porch as well as to rear screened porch.    The MAIN level features the  spacious primary bedroom suite with a walk-in-closet, den has fireplace (propane tank removed), kitchen with updated stainless appliances, including refrigerator,  breakfast nook with bay window, formal dining room, and an office/multipurpose room.  Owners relocated laundry to garage storage room.  This space could be sweet as a mudroom/book bag drop OR the plumbing can be turned back for laundry again.    UPPER level features two spacious bedrooms plus a bonus and GREAT walk-in-closets for extra storage.  NEW architectural shingles on house and outbuilding in July 2023. NEW paint in much of home in 2021. FDR, Office, and upstairs BRs were painted in 2023.  NEW luxury vinyl flooring in office, kitchen, breakfast room, upstairs hallway and upstairs bedroom in 2021. NEW stainless stove, DW, microwave, and refrigerator in 2021. Relocated laundry in 2021. NEW paint on garage doors Dec. 2023. NEW screen on screened porch in January 2024.  Hardwood floors in formal dining room, den, primary bedroom, hallway and foyer. Very spacious MASTER BEDROOM SUITE IN ON MAIN level. (2 sinks in Mba)  1/2 BATH is on MAIN level. Office/multi-use room is on MAIN level. Two spacious bedrooms and bonus are on upper level. Dream storage closets.  Numerous ceiling fans. Crown moldings. Dentil moldings. Chair railing. Plantation shutters/2" blinds. Pantry.  Garage has separate storage room separate from where laundry is.  10x12 outbuilding for more storage. NO CITY TAXES. Mere minutes to Lake Hartwell boat ramp, grocery, banking, churches, walking tracks, restaurants, shopping, I-85 access and more. IDEAL location for day-to-day living.  NO HOA!
